strings.Value: "Tartuccio, I recognize you. What is this new disguise â€” and why are you not dead?"
"Easy. Let's discuss this. No need to shed blood over some cart."
[Attack] "I've killed you once and I'll be happy to do it again!"
{n}The head of the gnome expedition wipes his brow and glares at the kobold.{/n} "This bastard was the one talking our ears off while the rest of them were trying to steal our cart."

"Koboldsss want thisss cart! Koboldsss ssshall have it!" {n}The horse skull hides most of the kobold's face, but you see his vicious eyes glinting through the empty sockets, staring at you.{/n} "By ordersss of myssself, the gloriousss King {d|Tartuk}Tartuk{/d}!" {n}The kobold pounds his chest with his fist.{/n}
{n}There's a... purple kobold on the river bank, who looks just like your old acquaintance, Tartuccio!{/n}
"KING Tartuk!" {n}The gnome looks at you and winks.{/n} "What do you say to a bit of regicide?"
"No. The gnome and hisss friendsss will sssee our rage! Shhhirdazzz!"
"How dare you ssspeak like that to King? Koboldsss, attack! Ssshirdazzz!"
"Ssso, the gnome invitesss sssome of hisss friendsss. Ssstupid, ssslow, sssluggish gnome."
